{"id":2384,"date":"2025-04-10T04:40:07","date_gmt":"2025-04-10T04:40:07","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/?p=2384"},"modified":"2025-04-11T03:10:57","modified_gmt":"2025-04-11T03:10:57","slug":"trai-nghiem-mot-ngay-lam-nha-bao-ton-nhi-cung-hoc-sinh-unis","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/vi\/trai-nghiem-mot-ngay-lam-nha-bao-ton-nhi-cung-hoc-sinh-unis\/","title":{"rendered":"TR\u1ea2I NGHI\u1ec6M M\u1ed8T NG\u00c0Y L\u00c0M NH\u00c0 B\u1ea2O T\u1ed2N NH\u00cd C\u00d9NG H\u1eccC SINH UNIS"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span class=\"TextRun SCXW81796008 BCX8\" lang=\"VI-VN\" xml:lang=\"VI-VN\" data-contrast=\"auto\"><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW81796008 BCX8\">Ng\u00e0y 22\/01 v\u1eeba qua, <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW81796008 BCX8\">WildAct<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW81796008 BCX8\"> \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng UNIS <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW81796008 BCX8\">Hanoi<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW81796008 BCX8\"> t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, gi\u00fap c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc sinh h\u00f3a th\u00e2n th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n nh\u00ed. D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a ch\u1ecb Trang Nguy\u1ec5n \u2013 nh\u00e0 s\u00e1ng l\u1eadp <\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SpellingErrorV2Themed SCXW81796008 BCX8\">WildAct<\/span><span class=\"NormalTextRun SCXW81796008 BCX8\">, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c th\u1ef1c ti\u1ec5n v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt hoang d\u00e3 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh quan s\u00e1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ph\u00fac l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p aria-level=\"3\"><b><i><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt hoang d\u00e3<\/span><\/i><\/b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;134245418&quot;:true,&quot;134245529&quot;:true,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559738&quot;:281,&quot;335559739&quot;:281}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh, WildAct \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc sinh UNIS \u0111\u1ebfn v\u01b0\u1eddn th\u00fa \u0111\u1ec3 tham gia v\u00e0o ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn tham quan, \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f2n l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp quan s\u00e1t c\u00e1c lo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt hoang d\u00e3, t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ed1ng, t\u1eadp t\u00ednh sinh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u00e0 ch\u00fang \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t.\u00a0<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, thay v\u00ec ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin qua s\u00e1ch v\u1edf hay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc sinh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadn m\u1eaft ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt s\u1ed1ng trong t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n nu\u00f4i nh\u1ed1t. Qua \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c em hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 <\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m ph\u00fac l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt <\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"auto\">v\u00e0<\/span><b><span data-contrast=\"auto\"> t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7<\/span><\/b><span data-contrast=\"auto\"> ch\u00fang trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.\u00a0<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p aria-level=\"3\"><em><b>H\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n<\/b>\u00a0<\/em><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a ch\u1ecb Trang Nguy\u1ec5n, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc sinh UNIS \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng quan s\u00e1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ph\u00fac l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt. B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch quan s\u00e1t h\u00e0nh vi, nh\u1eadn <\/span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">di\u1ec7n d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng ho\u1eb7c tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n t\u01b0 duy ph\u1ea3n bi\u1ec7n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n n\u00e2ng cao \u00fd th\u1ee9c tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc n\u00e0y gi\u00fap c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n theo c\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf h\u01a1n, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh t\u01b0 duy khoa h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 l\u00f2ng y\u00eau thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean.\u00a0<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-2385 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/a-day-in-the-life-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/a-day-in-the-life-1.png 3000w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/a-day-in-the-life-1-300x200.png 300w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/a-day-in-the-life-1-1024x683.png 1024w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/a-day-in-the-life-1-768x512.png 768w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/a-day-in-the-life-1-1536x1024.png 1536w, https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/a-day-in-the-life-1-2048x1365.png 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px\" \/><\/p>\n<p aria-level=\"3\"><em><b>Gieo m\u1ea7m \u00fd th\u1ee9c b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n t\u1eeb s\u1edbm<\/b>\u00a0<\/em><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">B\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia m\u00e0 c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 chung tay c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb. WildAct tin r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m <\/span><span data-contrast=\"auto\">th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc sinh ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn v\u1ec1 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a con ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean.\u00a0<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p aria-level=\"3\"><em><b>C\u00f9ng WildAct mang gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc h\u01a1n!<\/b>\u00a0<\/em><\/p>\n<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">V\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n lan t\u1ecfa t\u00ecnh y\u00eau thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 \u00fd th\u1ee9c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt hoang d\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ecdc sinh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, WildAct hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c nh\u1eefng ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n v\u00e0o gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00edch c\u1ef1c l\u00e2u d\u00e0i. N\u1ebfu tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, h\u00e3y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi WildAct \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng nhau mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u00fd ngh\u0129a cho h\u1ecdc sinh!<\/span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233117&quot;:false,&quot;134233118&quot;:false,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:0,&quot;335559737&quot;:0,&quot;335559738&quot;:240,&quot;335559739&quot;:240,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ng\u00e0y 22\/01 v\u1eeba qua, WildAct \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng UNIS Hanoi t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, gi\u00fap c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc sinh h\u00f3a th\u00e2n th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 b\u1ea3o t\u1ed3n nh\u00ed. D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a ch\u1ecb Trang Nguy\u1ec5n \u2013 nh\u00e0 s\u00e1ng l\u1eadp WildAct, c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2385,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[43],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-2384","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-moi-nhat"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2384","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2384"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2384\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2425,"href":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2384\/revisions\/2425"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2385"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2384"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2384"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wildact-vn.org\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2384"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}